de.wirecard.epos.model.sale.response.cardata

Class EmvCardDataResponse

  • de.wirecard.epos.model.sale.response.cardata.EmvCardDataResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CardDataResponse

    public class EmvCardDataResponse
implements CardDataResponse

    When processing EMV card the response will in addition to the common attributes also contain the EMV data returned by the issuer (processing network). We also need to return AID, Application Label and Cardholder Name which are obtained from the EMV request data.
